name: Edema
title: Edema
description: "This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024."
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values reflect patients experiencing edema, a swelling caused by excess fluid trapped in the body's tissues.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify patients with Edema.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes Edema related SNOMED CT codes from Findings hierarchy.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes Edema related SNOMED CT codes from Disorder of body system (disorder) hierarchy.)
